| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5744 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: af48a304-6cc7-50a4-bdaf-f2b1664f2ad8"
